## 15. Frontend Logs & AI Insights — `api/logs.py` (99 lines)

**File:** [logs.py](file:///Users/likhith./Veliora.AI_backend./api/logs.py)

| Endpoint | Method | Purpose |
|----------|--------|---------|
| `/api/logs/frontend-error` | POST | Receives frontend JavaScript errors (message, stack trace, browser, URL) for server-side logging |
| `/api/logs/dashboard-insights` | POST | Accepts merged telemetry+analytics payload, calls `generate_dashboard_insights()` via Gemini. Returns `{narrative, prediction, suggestions}`. Loaded lazily after dashboard renders for instant page load. |
| `/api/logs/insight-feedback` | POST | Records user feedback on AI-generated insights (`{user_id, insight_text, is_accurate}`) into `insight_feedbacks` table |

